{"tid":818114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港台灣前無加「中國」 官媒玻璃心：這是甚麼意思？","createTime":"2018-09-14T01:24:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T02:55:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7d28b99d4b8c54dc11933da08c98d068c8ef0811","tid":818114,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T01:24:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180914/20499437\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180914%2F20499437&d=AAikRAnnkpmqLFbgyV%2BMLP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=81e4a145\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180914%2F20499437&h=ef017d7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180914/20499437</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年09月14日 <br />\n<br />\n香港台灣前無加「中國」<br />\n官媒玻璃心：這是甚麼意思？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180914/large/a0301b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180914%2Flarge%2Fa0301b.gif&h=8718b93f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蘋果在發佈會上無在「香港」及「台灣」前標上「中國」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好好的一個手機發佈會，竟又打碎了內地網民玻璃心。昨蘋果公司在發佈會上公佈iPhone Xs的首發地區，列出「中國」、「香港」、「台灣」，但同時亦列出「美國」和「美國維爾京群島」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內媒轟香港　台灣前無標中國<br />\n<br />\n《環球時報》在微信公眾號大字標題炮轟：「蘋果，你發佈會上這是甚麼意思？」文章直斥：「既然蘋果公司知道在『維爾京群島』這個美國的海外屬地前標注『美國』，以區分『英屬維京群島』，為啥不能在『香港』和『臺灣』前也標注一個『China』，好讓更多人都清楚『香港』和『臺灣』都是中國的領土呢？」他們認為這種「雙重標準」，令中國消費感覺不被尊重。<br />\n<br />\n官媒說得義憤填膺，但網民一語道破：「少賣一個腎算好了，還指望抵制？」根據北京賽諾市場研究公司在7月的報告，蘋果手機今年頭半年的銷售額是1,727億人民幣（約1,977億港元），比第二位的OPPO及第三的Vivo加起來都高。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n新iPhone接受預訂　貴港逾千元內地Xs吹淡風<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n港人憑籃球App登發佈會大台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港人憑籃球App登發佈會大台<br />\n<br />\n先達店主看淡：僅可短炒<br />\n<br />\n新iPhone接受預訂貴港逾千元　內地Xs吹淡風"},{"pid":"b898fcd193237849ad7461c5ca04c757b2a55f83","tid":818114,"uid":198216,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T01:44:28.000Z","msg":"唔好幫襯囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57a5a7409972da558eb9d93859a6043798d3e226","tid":818114,"uid":19165,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T02:09:39.000Z","msg":"因為有US Virgin Islands 同UK Virgin Islands 所以要分開. 例如Gibraltar 就無寫UK Gibraltar, 因為係人都知. 中国眼光短如豆釘, 就係盯住自己隻腳, 真垃圾"},{"pid":"c2d3cb4432474b44d4508e796e200d81f38143f4","tid":818114,"uid":38366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T02:18:19.000Z","msg":"有種就唔好買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d71ba847d408c0e5b8a0fb4010f7a4bddd255e00","tid":818114,"uid":154502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T02:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/14/103357_c45b796f6ab9debb8ab6592a507dea48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F14%2F103357_c45b796f6ab9debb8ab6592a507dea48.jpg&h=b3644e69&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d0d446e22671dd16c51ae15815ae9a4a90a5561","tid":818114,"uid":182314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T02:48:18.000Z","msg":"唔想做你生意咯，仲問"},{"pid":"849726245a129a2bf756c82687b0aa0b148d5205","tid":818114,"uid":60145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T02:52:23.000Z","msg":"因為US Virgin Island 同Virgin Island 係唔同囉<br />\n月<br />\n同埋有寫埋Puerto Rico 即係唔係列主權國家囉   美國已經好小心"},{"pid":"3077c515bab40b22c5549122016584308687f865","tid":818114,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T02:55:21.000Z","msg":"人哋夠冇寫美國波多黎各啦"}]}